   857‚Üí#### `P._` wildcard
   859‚ÜíThe `P._` pattern will match any value. You can also use `P.any`, which is an alias to `P._`.
   860‚Üí
   861‚Üí```ts
   862‚Üíimport { match, P } from 'ts-pattern';
   863‚Üí
   864‚Üíconst input = 'hello';
   865‚Üí
