  1623‚Üí### `P.infer`
  1625‚Üí`P.infer<typeof somePattern>` lets you infer a type of value from a type of pattern.
  1626‚Üí
  1627‚ÜíIt's particularly useful when validating an API response.
  1628‚Üí
